Package: biofree.qyKEGGtools
Type: Package
Title: Smart Offline KEGG Enrichment Tool with Auto Update
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: person("Qiaoyu", "Chen", email = "persist2021@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides offline KEGG enrichment analysis with automatic local database update (via createKEGGdb) and optional GitHub self-update. Compatible with clusterProfiler, supports human (hsa) and mouse (mmu).
